    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const org = $input.first().json.organization || {};\nconst jobTitle = $('Webhook').first().json.body['Job Title '] || 'Unknown';\n\nconst userMessage = `Evaluate this company against our ICP and return a JSON assessment.\n\nICP DEFINITION:\n- Industry: B2B SaaS, FinTech, HR Tech, AI/Tech, or Professional Services\n- Company size: 50-10000 employees (no upper limit penalty — larger companies are stronger fits)\n- Geography: US or UK preferred but not required\n- Signals: Modern tech stack, growth-stage or established SaaS, has a sales or revenue team\n- Job title signals: VP, Director, Head of, C-suite, Founder, or RevOps/GTM roles\n\nSCORING GUIDE — be decisive:\n- Score 8-10 = Hot: clear B2B SaaS or FinTech company with 100+ employees and a sales team\n- Score 5-7 = Warm: B2B company but missing 1-2 key criteria\n- Score 1-4 = Cold: consumer company, tiny company under 20 employees, or no clear sales motion\n\nCRITICAL EXAMPLES — use these as your calibration:\n- Rippling (HR SaaS, 3000+ employees, US) = fit_score 9, fit_tier Hot\n- Ramp (FinTech SaaS, 1000+ employees, US) = fit_score 9, fit_tier Hot\n- Notion (B2B SaaS, 1000+ employees, US, productivity and collaboration tool) = fit_score 8, fit_tier Hot\n- A 3-person health coaching company = fit_score 2, fit_tier Cold\n\nWhen in doubt between Hot and Warm, choose Hot if the company is clearly B2B SaaS or FinTech with 100+ employees.\n\nCOMPANY DATA:\nCompany Name: ${org.name || 'Unknown'}\nIndustry: ${org.industry || 'Unknown'}\nEmployee Count: ${org.estimated_num_employees || 'Unknown'}\nAnnual Revenue: ${org.organization_revenue_printed || 'Unknown'}\nTech Stack: ${(org.technology_names || []).join(', ')}\nDescription: ${org.short_description || 'Unknown'}\nFounded: ${org.founded_year || 'Unknown'}\nFunding Stage: ${org.latest_funding_stage || 'Unknown'}\n\nJOB TITLE SUBMITTED: ${jobTitle}\n\nReturn exactly this JSON structure and nothing else:\n{\n  \"fit_score\": <integer 1-10>,\n  \"fit_tier\": \"<Hot|Warm|Cold>\",\n  \"fit_reasoning\": \"<2 sentences max explaining the score>\",\n  \"icp_matches\": [\"<list of criteria this company meets>\"],\n  \"icp_gaps\": [\"<list of criteria this company misses>\"],\n  \"suggested_action\": \"<Book meeting immediately|Enroll in nurture sequence|Disqualify>\",\n  \"personalization_hook\": \"<one specific observation about this company to use in outreach>\"\n}`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { user_message: userMessage } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        624,
        0
      ],
      "id": "cd83bbe4-e316-40b0-8c83-bb1df1a5b95c",
      "name": "Build OpenAI Prompt"
